{"tid":1891763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Trump不支持接收患「武漢肺炎」的美國公民回國","createTime":"2020-02-22T05:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T08:43:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4da7278995045db2d6105e7e211ad47570ad4523","tid":1891763,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"原來(美國國務院)接走鑽石公主郵輪班美籍人仕, 係有病個十四位都接走的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1886306/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1886306/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》報導:<br />\n<br />\n-據悉美國國務院係獨自決定接走鑽石公主郵輪果14位患「武漢肺炎」的美國公民, 無知會Donald Trump.<br />\n- Donald Trump知道呢個決定後, 有所不滿. Donald Trump話佢只同意接收健康的美國公民回國, 但不支持接收患「武漢肺炎」的美國公民回國. &nbsp;<br />\n- Trump政府對「武漢肺炎」高度重視. 係過去2星期, &nbsp;Trump政府已經開左10次會議, &nbsp;諗計防範「武漢肺炎」在美國社會蔓延.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-was-not-told-coronavirus-infected-americans-would-be-flown-home-from-cruise-ship/2020/02/21/ae58b24c-54be-11ea-b119-4faabac6674f_story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-was-not-told-coronavirus-infected-americans-would-be-flown-home-from-cruise-ship%2F2020%2F02%2F21%2Fae58b24c-54be-11ea-b119-4faabac6674f_story.html&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=f4daed3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-was-not-told-coronavirus-infected-americans-would-be-flown-home-from-cruise-ship/2020/02/21/ae58b24c-54be-11ea-b119-4faabac6674f_story.html</a>"},{"pid":"0f524026720c7b3ea1f4ac8533f63ca32e0c9214","tid":1891763,"uid":126621,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"我都唔支持<br />\n帶毒回鄉不肖子"},{"pid":"6f6358449e956d01ff5751eae638b4215a7701a2","tid":1891763,"uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:33:24.000Z","msg":"其實好正路<br />\n患「武漢肺炎」, 真係唔好番美國住比較好"},{"pid":"5245a62c08d870045fdc